        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 36 of the MONEY program. The script works with the specific discomfort of a full account: the part of you that tenses when the number is high, that waits for a bill to arrive, that can't quite let the balance feel normal.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
